isComplementaryErrorPage

protected boolean isComplementaryErrorPage(java.lang.Class<? extends org.apache.wicket.Page> pageClassParam)
This method may be overridden to check if a page is a custom complementary error page. For example, these pages may be shown in case of specific exceptions.

Parameters:
pageClassParam - The page.
Returns:
true if the page is a custom complementary error page, false else.
